name: __EMetasoundFrontendLiteralType
doc:
The type of a given literal for an input value.

The EMetasoundFrontendLiteralType's are matched to Metasound::ELiteralType`s
by giving them the same value. This supports easy conversion from one type to
another.

Boolean: < A value of None expresses that an object being constructed with a literal should be default constructed.
BooleanArray: < A NoneArray expresses the number of objects to be default constructed.
